<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta name="color-scheme" content="light dark" />
    <meta name="supported-color-schemes" content="light dark" />
    <title>Screening Scheduled - <%= jobTitle %></title>
    <style>
      :root {
        color-scheme: light dark;
        supported-color-schemes: light dark;
      }
      @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
        .email-container { background-color: #1a1a1a !important; }
        .email-content { background-color: #2d2d2d !important; color: #e0e0e0 !important; }
        .text-primary { color: #e0e0e0 !important; }
        .text-secondary { color: #b0b0b0 !important; }
        .header-text { color: #ffffff !important; }
        .footer { background-color: #2d2d2d !important; color: #b0b0b0 !important; }
        .footer a { color: #60a5fa !important; }
        .info-box { background-color: #374151 !important; }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #e8eef3;">
    <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" class="email-container" style="background-color: #e8eef3;">
      <tr>
        <td style="padding: 40px 20px;">
          <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
            <!-- Main Content Container -->
            <tr>
              <td class="email-content" style="background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);">
                
                <!-- Logo Header -->
                <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%">
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 32px 32px 24px 32px; text-align: center;">
                      <img src="https://jobstack.org/email-assets/logo.svg" alt="Jobstack" width="120" height="58" style="display: block; margin: 0 auto;" />
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>

                <!-- Content -->
                <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%">
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 0 32px 32px 32px;">
                      
                      <h1 class="header-text" style="margin: 0 0 16px 0; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 600; color: #1a1a1a; line-height: 1.3;">Screening Interview Scheduled</h1>

                      <!-- Notification Banner -->
                      <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="margin: 0 0 24px 0;">
                        <tr>
                          <td style="padding: 24px; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #8b5cf6 0%, #7c3aed 100%); border-radius: 8px; text-align: center;">
                            <h2 style="margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 600; color: #ffffff;">Custom Screening Invitation</h2>
                            <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 16px; color: #ffffff;">You've been invited to screen a candidate for your position.</p>
                          </td>
                        </tr>
                      </table>

                      <!-- Job Info -->
                      <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" class="info-box" style="background-color: #f9fafb; border-radius: 8px; margin: 0 0 24px 0;">
                        <tr>
                          <td style="padding: 20px;">
                            <h3 style="margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: #1a1a1a;">Position: <%= jobTitle %></h3>
                            <p class="text-secondary" style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280;">Job ID: <%= jobId %></p>
                          </td>
                        </tr>
                      </table>

                      <!-- Candidate Info -->
                      <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="margin: 0 0 24px 0;">
                        <tr>
                          <td style="padding: 20px; background-color: #fff3cd; border-radius: 8px; border: 2px solid #ffc107;">
                            <h3 style="margin: 0 0 12px 0; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: #856404;">Candidate Information</h3>
                            <p style="margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-size: 15px; color: #856404;"><strong>Name:</strong> <%= candidateName %></p>
                            <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 15px; color: #856404;"><strong>Application ID:</strong> <%= applicationId %></p>
                          </td>
                        </tr>
                      </table>

                      <!-- Meeting Details -->
                      <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="margin: 0 0 24px 0;">
                        <tr>
                          <td style="padding: 20px; background-color: #f0f9ff; border-radius: 8px; border: 2px solid #0ea5e9;">
                            <h3 style="margin: 0 0 16px 0; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: #0c4a6e;">Meeting Details</h3>
                            
                            <div style="margin: 0 0 16px 0;">
                              <strong style="color: #0c4a6e;">Scheduled Date & Time:</strong><br>
                              <span style="color: #0c4a6e;"><%= scheduledDateTime %></span>
                            </div>

                            <% if (meetingLink) { %>
                            <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" style="margin: 0;">
                              <tr>
                                <td style="text-align: center;">
                                  <a href="<%= meetingLink %>" style="display: inline-block; background-color: #0ea5e9; color: #ffffff; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; padding: 12px 32px; border-radius: 6px;">Join Screening Interview</a>
                                </td>
                              </tr>
                            </table>
                            <% } %>
                          </td>
                        </tr>
                      </table>

                      <% if (prepInfo) { %>
                      <!-- Preparation Info -->
                      <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" class="info-box" style="background-color: #f9fafb; border-radius: 8px; margin: 0 0 24px 0;">
                        <tr>
                          <td style="padding: 20px;">
                            <h4 style="margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #1a1a1a;">Preparation Information:</h4>
                            <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 15px; color: #4a4a4a; white-space: pre-wrap;"><%= prepInfo %></p>
                          </td>
                        </tr>
                      </table>
                      <% } %>

                      <!-- Role Info -->
                      <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="margin: 0 0 24px 0;">
                        <tr>
                          <td style="padding: 20px; background-color: #eff6ff; border-radius: 8px; border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6;">
                            <h3 style="margin: 0 0 12px 0; font-size: 18px; font-weight: 600; color: #1e40af;">Your Role in This Screening</h3>
                            <p style="margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-size: 15px; color: #1e40af;"><strong>As the employer, you will:</strong></p>
                            <ul style="margin: 0 0 12px 0; padding-left: 20px; color: #1e40af;">
                              <li style="margin: 4px 0;">Conduct the screening interview with the candidate</li>
                              <li style="margin: 4px 0;">Assess the candidate's suitability for your position</li>
                              <li style="margin: 4px 0;">Ask relevant questions about their experience and qualifications</li>
                              <li style="margin: 4px 0;">Make the final decision on whether to hire this candidate</li>
                            </ul>
                            <p style="margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-size: 15px; color: #1e40af;"><strong>The Jobstack admin will:</strong></p>
                            <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: 20px; color: #1e40af;">
                              <li style="margin: 4px 0;">Join as an invigilator representing Jobstack</li>
                              <li style="margin: 4px 0;">Ensure the screening process is professional and fair</li>
                              <li style="margin: 4px 0;">Provide support and facilitate the conversation</li>
                              <li style="margin: 4px 0;">Record the outcome for Jobstack's records</li>
                            </ul>
                          </td>
                        </tr>
                      </table>

                      <!-- Important Reminders -->
                      <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="margin: 0 0 24px 0;">
                        <tr>
                          <td style="padding: 20px; background-color: #fef2f2; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #dc2626;">
                            <h4 style="margin: 0 0 12px 0; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; color: #991b1b;">Important Reminders</h4>
                            <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: 20px; color: #991b1b;">
                              <li style="margin: 4px 0;">Please join the meeting at the scheduled time</li>
                              <li style="margin: 4px 0;">Prepare your questions and evaluation criteria beforehand</li>
                              <li style="margin: 4px 0;">The admin will be present throughout the screening</li>
                              <li style="margin: 4px 0;">If you need to reschedule, contact Jobstack support immediately</li>
                            </ul>
                          </td>
                        </tr>
                      </table>

                      <!-- Thank You Banner -->
                      <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" style="margin: 0 0 24px 0;">
                        <tr>
                          <td style="padding: 16px; background-color: #d4edda; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #28a745; text-align: center;">
                            <p style="margin: 0; color: #155724;">
                              <strong>Thank you for using Jobstack's screening service!</strong><br>
                              We're here to help you find the perfect candidate.
                            </p>
                          </td>
                        </tr>
                      </table>

                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>

                <!-- Footer -->
                <table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%" class="footer" style="background-color: #f9fafb; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;">
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 32px 32px 24px 32px;">
                      
                      <p class="text-secondary" style="margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; color: #6b7280; text-align: center;">
                        This is an automated notification from Jobstack.
                      </p>

                      <p class="text-secondary" style="margin: 0 0 16px 0; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; color: #6b7280; text-align: center;">
                        Questions or need support? Get in touch with us at 
                        <a href="mailto:support@jobstack.org" style="color: #2563eb; text-decoration: underline;">support@jobstack.org</a>.<br>
                        Follow us on 
                        <a href="https://twitter.com/jobstack" style="color: #2563eb; text-decoration: none;">Twitter</a>, 
                        <a href="https://facebook.com/jobstack" style="color: #2563eb; text-decoration: none;">Facebook</a> and 
                        <a href="https://instagram.com/jobstack" style="color: #2563eb; text-decoration: none;">Instagram</a>.
                      </p>

                      <p class="text-secondary" style="margin: 0; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5; color: #9ca3af; text-align: center;">
                        Don't want any more emails from Jobstack? <a href="https://jobstack.org/unsubscribe" style="color: #2563eb; text-decoration: underline;">Unsubscribe</a>.
                      </p>

                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>

              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>
            color: #1e40af;
        }
        .important-note {
            background-color: #fef2f2;
            border: 1px solid #dc2626;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .important-note h4 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #991b1b;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">JobStack</div>
            <h1>Screening Interview Scheduled</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="notification-banner">
            <h2 style="margin: 0; font-size: 20px;">Custom Screening Invitation</h2>
            <p style="margin: 10px 0 0 0; font-size: 16px;">You've been invited to screen a candidate for your position.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="job-info">
            <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #1f2937;">Position: <%= jobTitle %></h3>
            <p style="color: #6b7280; margin-bottom: 0;">Job ID: <%= jobId %></p>
        </div>

        <div class="candidate-info">
            <h3>Candidate Information</h3>
            <p><strong>Name:</strong> <%= candidateName %></p>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 0;"><strong>Application ID:</strong> <%= applicationId %></p>
        </div>

        <div class="meeting-details">
            <h3>Meeting Details</h3>
            
            <div class="meeting-info">
                <strong>Scheduled Date & Time:</strong><br>
                <%= scheduledDateTime %>
            </div>

            <div class="meeting-info">
                <strong>Meeting Link:</strong><br>
                <a href="<%= meetingLink %>" class="meeting-link" target="_blank">Join Screening Interview</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <% if (prepInfo) { %>
        <div style="background-color: #f3f4f6; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;">
            <h4 style="margin-top: 0; color: #374151;">Preparation Information:</h4>
            <p style="margin-bottom: 0; color: #4b5563; white-space: pre-wrap;"><%= prepInfo %></p>
        </div>
        <% } %>

        <div class="role-info">
            <h3>Your Role in This Screening</h3>
            <p><strong>As the employer, you will:</strong></p>
            <ul style="color: #1e40af;">
                <li>Conduct the screening interview with the candidate</li>
                <li>Assess the candidate's suitability for your position</li>
                <li>Ask relevant questions about their experience and qualifications</li>
                <li>Make the final decision on whether to hire this candidate</li>
            </ul>
            <p><strong>The JobStack admin will:</strong></p>
            <ul style="color: #1e40af;">
                <li>Join as an invigilator representing JobStack</li>
                <li>Ensure the screening process is professional and fair</li>
                <li>Provide support and facilitate the conversation</li>
                <li>Record the outcome for JobStack's records</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="important-note">
            <h4>Important Reminders</h4>
            <ul style="color: #991b1b; margin: 10px 0;">
                <li>Please join the meeting at the scheduled time</li>
                <li>Prepare your questions and evaluation criteria beforehand</li>
                <li>The admin will be present throughout the screening</li>
                <li>If you need to reschedule, contact JobStack support immediately</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div style="background-color: #f0fdf4; border: 1px solid #16a34a; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;">
            <p style="margin: 0; color: #15803d; text-align: center;">
                <strong>Thank you for using JobStack's screening service!</strong><br>
                We're here to help you find the perfect candidate.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated notification from JobStack.</p>
            <p>If you have any questions, please contact our support team.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>